    <title>Hexo 升级</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/02/18/Hexo%20%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/02/18/Hexo%20%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/</id>
    <published>2020-02-18T09:51:30.570Z</published>
    <updated>2020-02-21T09:45:21.952Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><p>查看 node.js 和 npm 的版本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> node -v</span></span><br><span class="line">v8.11.2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> npm -v</span></span><br><span class="line">5.6.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将其升级到最新版本</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="升级-npm"><a href="#升级-npm" class="headerlink" title="升级 npm"></a>升级 npm</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g npm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>报错</p><p><img data-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LigerShuai/PictureSpace/master/blog/202002182047.png" alt=""></p><p>根据提示 <em>Please try running this command again as root/Administrator</em> 可知是权限不够，以管理员权限运行：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo npm install -g npm</span></span><br><span class="line">Password:</span><br><span class="line">/usr/local/bin/npx -&gt; /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npx-cli.js</span><br><span class="line">/usr/local/bin/npm -&gt; /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npm-cli.js</span><br><span class="line">+ npm@6.13.7</span><br><span class="line">added 326 packages, removed 368 packages and updated 59 packages in 10.401s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看版本，已升级到 6.13.7, That’s OK.</p><p><strong>升级 Node</strong></p><blockquote><p>sudo npm cache clean -f //清除nodejs的cache：<br>sudo npm install -g n //使用npm安装n模块<br>npm view node versions // node所有版本<br>sudo n latest // 升级到最新版本<br>sudo n stable // 升级到稳定版本<br>sudo n xx.xx // 升级到具体版本号</p></blockquote><p>首先清除 Node.js 的缓存，然后使用 npm 安装 Node.js 的多版本管理器 n 模块，最后升级到稳定版本。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo npm cache clean -f</span></span><br><span class="line">Password:</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN using --force I sure hope you know what you are doing.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo npm install -g n</span></span><br><span class="line">/usr/local/bin/n -&gt; /usr/local/lib/node_modules/n/bin/n</span><br><span class="line">+ n@6.2.0</span><br><span class="line">added 1 package from 4 contributors in 9.615s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo n stable</span></span><br><span class="line">  installing : node-v12.16.1</span><br><span class="line">       mkdir : /usr/local/n/versions/node/12.16.1</span><br><span class="line">       fetch : https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.16.1/node-v12.16.1-darwin-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line">   installed : v12.16.1 (with npm 6.13.4)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看版本，已安装 12.16.1，That’s OK.</p><h2 id="升级-Hexo"><a href="#升级-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="升级 Hexo"></a>升级 Hexo</h2><blockquote><p>先全局升级hexo-cli：-g表示全局升级。hexo本身是一个静态博客生成工具，具备编译Markdown、拼接主题模板、生成 HTML、上传 Git 等基本功能。hexo-cli能够将这些功能封装为命令，提供给用户通过hexo server / hexo deploy等命令调用的模块。CLI = Command Line Interface命令行界面。</p></blockquote><p>查看 hexo 当前版本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo -v</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo: 3.7.1</span><br><span class="line">hexo-cli: 1.1.0</span><br><span class="line">os: Darwin 19.2.0 darwin x64</span><br><span class="line">node: 12.16.1</span><br><span class="line">v8: 7.8.279.23-node.31</span><br><span class="line">uv: 1.34.0</span><br><span class="line">zlib: 1.2.11</span><br><span class="line">brotli: 1.0.7</span><br><span class="line">ares: 1.15.0</span><br><span class="line">modules: 72</span><br><span class="line">nghttp2: 1.40.0</span><br><span class="line">napi: 5</span><br><span class="line">llhttp: 2.0.4</span><br><span class="line">http_parser: 2.9.3</span><br><span class="line">openssl: 1.1.1d</span><br><span class="line">cldr: 35.1</span><br><span class="line">icu: 64.2</span><br><span class="line">tz: 2019c</span><br><span class="line">unicode: 12.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="使用-npm-自动更新"><a href="#使用-npm-自动更新" class="headerlink" title="使用 npm 自动更新"></a>使用 npm 自动更新</h4><ol><li><p>升级 hexo-cli</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo npm i hexo-cli -g</span></span><br><span class="line">Password:</span><br><span class="line">/usr/local/bin/hexo -&gt; /usr/local/lib/node_modules/hexo-cli/bin/hexo</span><br><span class="line">+ hexo-cli@3.1.0</span><br><span class="line">added 20 packages from 10 contributors, removed 116 packages and updated 36 packages in 21.338s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使用npm-check 检查依赖模块的更新</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo npm install -g npm-check</span><br><span class="line">npm-check</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到，依赖模块的更新信息如下：</p><p><img data-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LigerShuai/PictureSpace/master/blog/202002191856.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>使用 npm-upgrade 来更新 hexo 依赖模块</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo npm install -g npm-upgrade</span><br><span class="line">npm-upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时会有个选择菜单供你选择是否升级依赖包：</p><img data-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LigerShuai/PictureSpace/master/blog/202002191910.png" style="zoom: 25%;" /><p>全部 Yes.</p><p>再使用 <code>npm-check</code> 查看，发现已全部更新。</p><p>或者查看 hexo 目录下的 package.json 文件，确认依赖包已全部更新。</p></li><li><p>更新 hexo</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看 hexo 版本，已更新。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo -v</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo: 4.2.0 # 已更新</span><br><span class="line">hexo-cli: 3.1.0</span><br><span class="line">os: Darwin 19.2.0 darwin x64</span><br><span class="line">node: 12.16.1</span><br><span class="line">v8: 7.8.279.23-node.31</span><br><span class="line">uv: 1.34.0</span><br><span class="line">zlib: 1.2.11</span><br><span class="line">brotli: 1.0.7</span><br><span class="line">ares: 1.15.0</span><br><span class="line">modules: 72</span><br><span class="line">nghttp2: 1.40.0</span><br><span class="line">napi: 5</span><br><span class="line">llhttp: 2.0.4</span><br><span class="line">http_parser: 2.9.3</span><br><span class="line">openssl: 1.1.1d</span><br><span class="line">cldr: 35.1</span><br><span class="line">icu: 64.2</span><br><span class="line">tz: 2019c</span><br><span class="line">unicode: 12.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h4 id="手动更新"><a href="#手动更新" class="headerlink" title="手动更新"></a>手动更新</h4><ol><li><p>查看有哪些需要更新</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> npm outdated</span></span><br><span class="line">Package                  Current  Wanted  Latest  Location</span><br><span class="line">hexo                       3.7.1   3.9.0   4.2.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-deployer-git          0.3.1   0.3.1   2.1.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-archive     0.1.5   0.1.5   1.0.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-category    0.1.3   0.1.3   1.0.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-index       0.2.1   0.2.1   1.0.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-tag         0.2.0   0.2.0   1.0.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-renderer-ejs          0.3.1   0.3.1   1.0.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-renderer-marked       0.3.2   0.3.2   2.0.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-renderer-stylus       0.3.3   0.3.3   1.1.0  hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">hexo-server                0.2.2   0.2.2   1.0.0  hexo-site</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ol start="2"><li><p>进入 Blog 目录，修改 package.json 文件，将版本号改为最新</p><blockquote><p>{<br>  “name”: “hexo-site”,<br>  “version”: “0.0.0”,<br>  “private”: true,<br>  “hexo”: {</p><pre><code>&quot;version&quot;: &quot;4.2.0&quot;</code></pre><p>  },<br>  “dependencies”: {</p><pre><code>&quot;hexo&quot;: &quot;^4.2.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-deployer-git&quot;: &quot;^2.1.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-generator-archive&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-generator-category&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-generator-index&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-generator-tag&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-renderer-ejs&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-renderer-marked&quot;: &quot;^2.0.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-renderer-stylus&quot;: &quot;^1.1.0&quot;,&quot;hexo-server&quot;: &quot;^1.0.0&quot;</code></pre><p>  }<br>}</p></blockquote><p>然后更新即可。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>参考：</p><ul><li><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3doamttL2FydGljbGUvZGV0YWlscy84MTA4ODUxOA==" title="https://blog.csdn.net/whjkm/article/details/81088518">Hexo版本升级和Next主题升级之坑<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></p></li><li><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly90b21teS5uZXQuY24vMjAxOC8wMi8yNi91cGdyYWRlLWhleG8tdG8tdjMtNS0wLw==" title="https://tommy.net.cn/2018/02/26/upgrade-hexo-to-v3-5-0/">将 Hexo 升级到 v3.5.0<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;准备&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#准备&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;准备&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;准备&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;查看 node.js 和 npm 的版本&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt; node -v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;v8.11.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt; npm -v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5.6.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;将其升级到最新版本&lt;/p&gt;
    
